Package neupaths.stim

package neupaths.stim
Stimulus types for Java primitive types.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BooleanStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a boolean value.
    ByteStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a byte value.
    CharacterStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a char value.
    DateStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a Date value.
    DoubleStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a double value.
    FloatStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a float value.
    IntegerStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates an int value.
    LongStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a long value.
    ShortStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a short value.
    SignalStimulus
    An alias for BooleanStimulus where true means on and false means off.
    StringStimulus
    A NeuPaths stimulus type that encapsulates a java.lang.String value.

    An alias for DateStimulus.
